.RS 4
Show copying policy and exit
.P
.RE
\fB-l\fR, \fB--localtime\fR
.RS 4
Use local time rather than UTC
.P
.RE
\fB-o\fR \fIOUTPUT\fR, \fB--output\fR=\fIOUTPUT\fR
.RS 4
Path to output file
.P
.RE
RFC 3339 timestamps are given with µs precision.
.P
